Mga Pinakamahabang One Night Stand is a collection of four short films exploring themes of fidelity, relationships and true love in a world filled with complex societal norms permeating personal spaces. (1) "Wait Water Wait" directed by Crisaldo Pablo (2) "Balot Ko" directed by Harbi Estradough (3) "Ang Pinakamahabang One Night Standand" directed by Eduardo Roy Jr (4) "Tutok" directed by Crisaldo Pablo.
